Specify the following variables during init:

   VENDOR_NAME, PROJECT_DESCRIPTION, VENDOR_CONTACT

VENDOR_NAME is required and important. The other two values are for
CMakePackage.cmake.

e.g.

```
mulle-sde init --common mulle-sde:extension \
               -DVENDOR="my-vendor" \
               -DPROJECT_DESCRIPTION="my extension"
               -DVENDOR_CONTACT="you@my-vendor.org" extension
```
